  Accela Automation
  File: RunReportScript
 
  Accela, Inc.
  Copyright (C): 2007-2014
 
  Description:
  Provides the root of the object model exposed to scripts running
  on the scripting engine. Known to the script writer as the top
  level "aa" object.
